rows.label: tlk70000027_02_msg0001
rows.name:
What does this Metsu fellow think
he's doing?!

rows.label: tlk70000027_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Does he suppose he can wreak havoc
in this town with impunity?

rows.label: tlk70000027_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Still, there's no point getting all
frazzled about it.

rows.label: tlk70000027_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Hand-wringing and crying to Prince
Adel will have to wait. We have a
great deal of work to do!
